ROADMAP TO CONQUER THE WORLD:
1. Test the stylesheets a bit more.
2. install saxon8 on the ebn machine
3. Patch krazy2ebn.pl to let it output xml and transform that to ebn-html.
4. Make all above work.
5. Remove all (ebn)html stuff from krazy2.
6. (Re)design the database.
7. Create another stylesheets which does xml -> sql
8. Write some html reports showing statistics retrieved from the db.
